Overview

Sola Heavy/Duty is excited to introduce the new GL Power Supply Series to replace the current GL Series. The new Series covers power ratings from 25 to 500 watts providing a broader range of AC/DC power supply solutions for use in various industrial and medical applications. These compact and low profile switchers offer universal input voltages with no switches or jumpers. They are for higher volume worldwide applications requiring very high reliability and standard footprint size.

  • Industry Standard Footprints
  • Universal Input
  • Full Power to 50°C
  • High Demonstrate MTBF
  • Automatic Overvoltage Protection
  • Overload Protection
  • Two Year Limited Warranty
  • EN61000-3-2 Compliance
  • Medical Approvals
Specifications
Brand/SeriesGL Series
ConfigurationOpen Frame
Dimensions4. 25 × 8. 5 × 1. 5 In.
Mounting TypePanel
Number of Outputs5
OperationSwitching
Output5VDC@15A, 12VDC@2. 6A, 15VDC@2. 5A, -12VDC@2A, -15VDC@2. 5A
Power, Output150 W
Primary TypeAC-DC
Special FeaturesLow-Profile, High Demonstrated MTBF, Automatic Overvoltage Protection, Overload Protection, Built-in EMI Filtering, 2-Years Limited Warranty, Remote Sense, Power Fail and DC Good Signals
TypeEmbedded
Voltage, Input85-132/170-264 VAC
Voltage, Output5 VDC, 12 VDC, -12 VDC, 5 to 25 VDC, -5 to 25 VDC

Overview

These high power, modular power supplies, from 1500 through 2000 watts, are capable of up to 12 independent outputs. Modular design makes these units easy to customize for unusual voltage and power combinations. All units have power factor corrected inputs, an end-mounted fan for cooling and a variety of built-in signals and controls. High-reliability and a flexible design make these an excellent choice for process control and semiconductor fabrication applications.

  • For Industrial and Industrial Computing Applications
  • Universal AC: SH1 and SH2 Models — 85-264 VAC Single Phase; SH3 Models — 180-264 VAC Three Phase
  • Power Factor Correction to Meet IEC1000-3-2
  • Regulation: Single Outputs — <2. 0%; Multiple Outputs — <3. 3%
  • Signals: Remote Inhibit Global and Individual Output, Global Power Good, AC Power Fail
  • Single Wire Current Share for Redundancy or Scalability
  • Screw Terminals/Bus Bars for Power Terminations; Molex-Type Connections for Signals (Mating Connectors Included)
  • Chassis Mounting
  • World-Wide Approvals — UL, CSA, TUV and CE
  • EMI Filter FCC Level B, CISPR 22 Level B, EN55022 Level B

480 VAC, 3% Impedance, SLR Series Line ReactorsSola/Hevi-Duty introduces DIN Rail mounted line reactors as the latest addition to a family of power quality products with a reputation for increasing industrial automation system performance. The SLR Series is a CE style, DIN Rail Mounted line reactor that provides safe, compact protection for high frequency drives and electronic equipment. The SLR inductive filter prevents damage to any three phase electronic system plagued by capacitor or large load switching. Reduces harmonics and input line distortion.

  • Compact, IP 20 Finger-Safe Packaging
  • Reduces Stress on Drive Components Keeping Drives Running Longer
  • Removes Harmonics and Helps Keep Line Voltage Smooth Through Notching
  • Eliminates Drive Cross-Talk and Interference
  • DIN Rail Mount Through 20 HP
  • Ten-Year Warranty

480 VAC, 3% Impedance, SLR Series Line ReactorsSola/Hevi-Duty introduces DIN Rail mounted line reactors as the latest addition to a family of power quality products with a reputation for increasing industrial automation system performance. The SLR Series is a CE style, DIN Rail Mounted line reactor that provides safe, compact protection for high frequency drives and electronic equipment. The SLR inductive filter prevents damage to any three phase electronic system plagued by capacitor or large load switching. Reduces harmonics and input line distortion.

  • Compact, IP 20 Finger-Safe Packaging
  • Reduces Stress on Drive Components Keeping Drives Running Longer
  • Removes Harmonics and Helps Keep Line Voltage Smooth Through Notching
  • Eliminates Drive Cross-Talk and Interference
  • DIN Rail Mount Through 20 HP
  • Ten-Year Warranty
